{"version": 2, "width": 120, "height": 35, "timestamp": 1711400000, "title": "The Intern — Kevin's First Day in Production"}
[0.1, "o", "\u001b[2m# Monday, 9:04 AM. Kevin has been at the company for 3 days.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.8, "o", "\u001b[2m# He's been trusted with his first production deployment. What could go wrong?\u001b[0m\r\n"]
